/ Banner
%section#banner
  .content
    %header
      %h2 BingBites
      %p
        Just food. Loads of lip licking Delicacies, Happiness.
        %br/
        There are no hoverboards or flying cars around.
        %br/
        Yet there's an easy way to find quick-lunch.
    %span.image
      = image_tag "pic0x.jpg"
  %a.goto-next.scrolly{:href => "#one"} Next

/ One
%section#one.spotlight.style1.bottom
  %span.image.fit.main
    = image_tag "pic02.jpg"
  .content
    .container
      .row
        .4u{:class => "12u$(medium)"}
          %header
            %h2 Welcome to BingBites
            %p
              Stay hungry. Stay foolish
              %br/
              So how it works ?
        .4u{:class => "12u$(medium)"}
          %ul
            %li SignIn to search the restaurants
            %li Pick the restaurant from the list
            %li Choose from the available categories
            %li Browse exhaustive list of cousines
            %li Find out Specialities Served for the day
            %li Review what you liked and what you didn't
        %div{:class => "4u$ 12u$(medium)"}
          %p
            We are trying to redefine how you search for food
            in the locality. Our goal is to serve you delicious
            food with events and seasonal specialties.
            %br/
            Do you love pleasant ambiance and peculiar meal
            that matches your taste of food for your mood?
            BingBites finds it for you at your fingertips.


  %a.goto-next.scrolly{:href => "#two"} Next
/ Two
%section#two.spotlight.style2.right
  %span.image.fit.main
    = image_tag "pic03.jpg"
  .content
    %header
      %h2 Enabling restaurants to create amazing experiences.
      %p Every restaurant we listed is a speciality in itself providing services to bring you delight.
    %p With dedicated engagement and collaboration tools, we're enabling restaurants to spend more time focusing on food itself, which translates directly to better dining experiences.
    %ul.actions
      %li
        %a.button{:href => "#"} Learn More
  %a.goto-next.scrolly{:href => "#three"} Next
/ Three
%section#three.spotlight.style3.left
  %span.image.fit.main.bottom
    = image_tag "pic04.jpg"
  .content
